{"tid":2011332,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(內地SHOW)劉德華+周杰倫聯手向醫護致敬 　教你睇華仔等巨星5.11網上騷","createTime":"2020-05-11T02:29:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T15:29:16.000Z","uid":224375,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d6f200429efe48a0e360b012d4dd2e098250e311","tid":2011332,"uid":224375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T02:29:25.000Z","msg":"許冠傑、郭富城接連在香港舉行網上音樂會，為港人打氣，成為熱話。不少樂迷期待下一個開網上騷的天王巨星，原來劉德華已低調參予一個內地網上抗疫騷，將在今晚（5月11日）晚上7:30參予「致敬白衣天使公益雲演唱會」，連同周杰倫、梁詠琪、蕭敬騰、孫燕姿等多位華語巨星演出。<br />\n<br />\n「致敬白衣天使公益雲演唱會」由內地多間機構包括微博、人民日報等主辦，主題是向醫護致敬，除劉德華外，其他演出單位來自中港台三地歌手，包括周杰倫、梁詠琪、莫文蔚、林俊傑、蕭敬騰、孫燕姿、梁靜茹、伍佰等演出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2639515/?r=mcsdfb&amp;fbclid=IwAR2JpmCNcOVQpzN-9jxCX1dg2QFMx8GWEn5ezPybBOsp0Fd0xldCgclMw7I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2639515%2F%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb%26fbclid%3DIwAR2JpmCNcOVQpzN-9jxCX1dg2QFMx8GWEn5ezPybBOsp0Fd0xldCgclMw7I&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnyR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=8701f260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2639515/?r=mcsdfb&amp;fbclid=IwAR2JpmCNcOVQpzN-9jxCX1dg2QFMx8GWEn5ezPybBOsp0Fd0xldCgclMw7I</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母香港唔駛幫????!!!!</span>"},{"pid":"956b8442920e62d134a0e2eb093c8955d7b6ab7e","tid":2011332,"uid":213877,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T02:33:17.000Z","msg":"奶共華名不虛傳"},{"pid":"c2a5e3551b26ca675e79b9a311abf509966fdae6","tid":2011332,"uid":70487,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T02:34:49.000Z","msg":"舐共偽人一次過block晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e628b835eca4e0f6193b4dbfaad9ba8b66088feb","tid":2011332,"uid":356842,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T02:35:13.000Z","msg":